DATAMOSH on an iPhone. The unique effect that inspired artists like Kanye West or A AP Mob to glitch their music videos is now available in Glitché. Decode up to three videos from your camera roll simultaneously or experiment with real time recording. It s also a powerful crypto art tool: the result of DATAMOSH is based on random data and cannot be recreated. New PIXEL and SORT filters complementing the set of irreplaceable Glitché effects. Glitch text generator to randomly style each letter. Huge set of new fonts. Designed text can be copied and pasted into any other app for example to a TikTok profile or an Instagram comment . New AR mask in the shape of the Glitché logo. Tons of improvements to filters and overall application performance. Redesigned interface animated toolbars and much more. Follow us on social media as Travis Scott and Post Malone do . Tag GlitcheApp so we can repost. If you can t use or find in app purchases that you bought try to restore them with Restore purchases button. Found a bug Tell us: info glitche.com Thank you for being with us! Glitché Team

Face filters are so last decade. It s time to change the game. Use our new SCLPTRs in AR or mix them with your content to create outstanding TikTok and Instagram stories Try brand new PHOTO filters with authentic hardcore glitches: JPG and PNG Try new CAMERA section: hold the button to shoot a video or tap it to make a photo Thank you for supporting us. Don t forget to tag your art Glitche to be featured. More to come soon!

Thank you for your support and reviews. We appreciate all of your feedback and work hard to make our app even better. This updated version features: Bug fixes and stability improvements. We brought back the old SORT filter.

Also: iOS 13 support Tons of bug fixes Overall improvements More updates coming soon!

Hi! First of all we want to thank: Radiohead for the OK Computer OKNOTOK 1997 2017 promo video created with Glitché. Gorillaz and personally Jamie Hewlett for using Glitché to create the official Humanz artbook apparel and Gorillaz s stage design videos. Marilyn Manson for the official Tattooed in Reverse music video with the Glitché filters in the beginning. Demna Gvasalia and Vetements for using Glitché for the Summer 2018 promos. Nick Knight and SHOWstudio for choosing Glitché to create the groundbreaking ALYX x Nike collaboration photoshoot for the summer issue of the 032c mag. Louis Vuitton for the Men s Summer 2018 Collection promo videos created with Glitché. Lil Uzi Vert s XO Tour Llif3 producer TM88 for using Glitché for his rad Instagram stories. Gigi Hadid John Mayer Prefuse73 Brodinski Alison Wonderland and all the Glitché users for your art! And of course Apple for featuring Glitché in App Culture and App of the Day in so many countries from Germany to Japan. We earned No. 1 on the AppStore in 89 countries! WHAT S NEW. FILTERS: RAD an original color shifting scanner with 3 modes. VIBE creates beautiful light paintings and accidentally blurred photos. DEPTH for a depth map of your portrait mode photos. VENOM for volumetric digital distortions. NEW INSTRUMENTS: Video Filter Trimmer. Allows applying different filters to the different parts of the same video opening unlimited possibilities for editing and montage. URL import. Remix most popular GIFs or photos you found on Giphy Instagram or any other place. Professional layer blending modes: Darken Multiply Lighten Screen Add Overlay Difference and Divide for the most unexpected and satisfying results. Works for texts too. Not just a font: use Bitmoji Kimoji or any other keyboards to up your sticker game to a whole new level. IMPROVEMENTS: iPhone X and iPad Pro support. New beautiful and functional design. Export screen. Swipe up to share or swipe down to save. New prices. Use all the instruments and updates of the app for under 2. Autosave. Allows recovering edits after accidental quit or crash. We fixed a lot of bugs and made Glitché work faster and be more stable. A new update is on the way! PLEASE USE RESTORE BUTTON TO RESTORE PREVIOUS PURCHASES. If you liked this version please give us five stars on the AppStore page. Follow us on Instagram and Twitter like Post Malone does : GlitcheApp

Hi! We have a lot of news for you! First of all we would like to thank the Gorillaz and personally Jamie Hewlett for choosing our app to create the artworks and the global promos for their new album Humanz. Eight official singles with covers created using Glitché are available on iTunes the amazing videos for the new tracks also created in Glitché have already been viewed more than 11 000 000 times on YouTube and a lot of GIFs created by the band in our app have flown across the twitter from Radio Beats 1 to Jean Michel Jarre who also took part in the recording of Humanz. Even the avatar the Gorillaz use on Facebook is animated using Glitché. It s unbelievable and we are very honoured to be a part of this story! Next: our congratulations to Travis Scott for getting his album Birds in the Trap Sing McKnight to platinum status! You probably remember that the cover for this album was created by the legendary photographer Nick Knight using Glitché. It is an honour and a joy to know that the creation of Glitché shall forever reside in the musical hall of fame! And last but not least thanks a million to: Kim Kardashian for choosing Glitché to promote her own Kimoji app Paramount Pictures for the Ghost In The Shell filter used almost 1 000 000 times by now Gucci Ghost Skepta and Run The Jewels for their art Lil Uzi Vert s XO Tour Llif3 producer TM88 who named Glitché the best app in the world. Thank you! XXXTENTACION for his touching message we love you too bro The Golden Filter for the Now We Get Lost video entirely created in Glitché as well as HYPEBEAST for the material about our app. And of course we would like to thank you dear friends for your five star ratings and reviews that help us move forward. In this version we fixed a lot of bugs and made Glitché work faster and be more stable. What s new: The BRUSH setting has become an independent filter combining the functions of LIQUIFY New DARK filter for exploring the dark sides of glitch art for camera photo and video editors Now it s enough to go to the next screen to apply the effect to the entire video without controlling the recording process manually. The long awaited feature We fixed the bug in which the video became shorter when adding new filters Latest photos and videos from the camera roll are now displayed on the main screen Lots of other improvements We are already working on a new version of Glitché. The result will surpass all expectations. Follow us on Instagram Twitter and Facebook GlitcheApp Use RESTORE button to restore previous purchases.

Dear friends we are thrilled to present you a new filter we have created in collaboration with Paramount Pictures and the team of the Ghost in the Shell film. Try yourself in the role of the characters of the cult anime and surprise your friends with your video posters of the most anticipated film of the year. Tag it with Glitche and GhostInTheShell to be featured! MORE NEW FEATURES: New and powerful SORT filter for endless experiments with pixel sorting Capture button in the Camera Filters: use it to start recording and focus on the adjusting of the effects Use the Camera icon in the Camera Filters to switch to photo mode. A long awaited feature ASCII filter for creating asci art New blue yellow color mode in CHNNLS SCREEN LCD BLUR and more New DASH mode in GRNDT New ZOOM filter for maximum zoom level New toolbar: fullscreen files look much better now Indication of removed color in the Layer Blending screen Access to the Camera Filters from the Export screen Bug fixes and overall improvement Endless inspiration and creativity Thank you for your feedback! It really helps. Don t forget to post all your works with Glitche so we can feature you! And happy glitchin!
